00:10:16,867 --> 00:10:19,328
Yowzers!

265
00:10:19,411 --> 00:10:22,164
> Hello, daddy!
Hello, mommy

266
00:10:22,247 --> 00:10:24,333
D It's so nice to be here
with you now J

267
00:10:24,416 --> 00:10:26,877
[ snoring ]

268
00:10:31,173 --> 00:10:33,133
Ohhhh!

269
00:10:37,054 --> 00:10:40,682
Boy, Jake left a scar on my head
the size of a nickel.

270
00:10:40,766 --> 00:10:43,143
I'll have to wear a hat now,
Margaret.

271
00:10:43,227 --> 00:10:46,104
Well, | think you'll look
good in one.

272
00:10:46,188 --> 00:10:48,524
MARGARET: Are you sure having
him next to Jermaine is safe?

273
00:10:48,607 --> 00:10:50,651
We don't even know what he is.

274
00:10:50,734 --> 00:10:52,110
[ smacks lips ]

275
00:10:52,194 --> 00:10:54,655
Of course we do, dear --
he's our boy.

276
00:10:54,738 --> 00:10:57,324
That he is.

277
00:10:57,407 --> 00:10:59,743
Yes, we've got one boy
that | gave birth to,

278
00:10:59,827 --> 00:11:01,495
and one boy
you gave birth to.

279
00:11:01,578 --> 00:11:03,121
Let's never tell him
how it happened.

280
00:11:03,205 --> 00:11:05,207
Agreed.

281
00:11:05,290 --> 00:11:07,876
And so they never told me.

282
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,670
Never told you what?

283
00:11:09,753 --> 00:11:12,673
| don't know.
They never told me. Ha!

284
00:11:13,882 --> 00:11:17,886
» Come along with me »

285
00:11:17,970 --> 00:11:21,974
And the butterflies and bees

286
00:11:22,057 --> 00:11:25,352
» We can wander through the forest J»

287
00:11:25,435 --> 00:11:29,857
2 And do so as we please »

288
00:11:29,940 --> 00:11:33,652
» Come along with me »

289
00:11:33,735 --> 00:11:36,572
D To a cliff under a tree »

290
00:11:40,409 --> 00:11:42,661
This party is so crazy!

